The best way I’ve found to pursue excellence in your craft is to join a community or mastermind with other creators - like Viral Video Club.

I played poker against one of the best players in the world. And I asked him what his chances of winning were. 

His answer shocked me. 

“25% or so”

One of the best that’s ever played against a bunch of amateurs. And he only has 25% chance of winning. 

Poker is like life - you cannot remove the luck.

But it’s crazy how much luck gets ironed out when you just don’t stop.
